# How Senior DevOps Engineers Troubleshoot (Golden Process)

Whenever production breaks, they follow this order:

### Step 1 — Check cluster

```
kubectl get nodes
```

### Step 2 — Check pods

```
kubectl get pods -A
```

### Step 3 — Describe resource

```
kubectl describe pod
```

### Step 4 — Check logs

```
kubectl logs
```

### Step 5 — Check events

```
kubectl get events
```

### Step 6 — Check networking

```
kubectl get svc
kubectl get endpoints
```

